text: What a beautiful send-off episode to Going Seventeen 2023. I really loved all the past content (as I'm binge watching them) and everything that was filmed this year. Also, lots of love to Seventeen always, and sending you best wishes for the tour and concert. SCoups, get well, take care of yourself, we miss you.
